perl-digest-hmac|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
perl-digest-hmac: perl-digest-hmac (Digest-HMAC Perl module)
perl-digest-hmac:
perl-digest-hmac: HMAC is used for message integrity checks between two parties that
perl-digest-hmac: share a secret key, and works in combination with some other Digest
perl-digest-hmac: algorithm, usually MD5 or SHA-1. The HMAC mechanism is described in
perl-digest-hmac: RFC 2104.
perl-digest-hmac: HMAC follow the common Digest:: interface, but the constructor takes
perl-digest-hmac: the secret key and the name of some other simple Digest:: as argument.
perl-digest-hmac:
perl-digest-hmac: http://search.cpan.org/dist/Digest-HMAC/
perl-digest-hmac: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
